@startuml State_Cancellation_Action
title Cancellation Action State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<approval>> LightYellow
    BackgroundColor<<ready>> LightBlue
    BackgroundColor<<active>> LightGreen
    BackgroundColor<<success>> PaleGreen
    BackgroundColor<<failure>> LightCoral
    BackgroundColor<<retry>> Wheat
}

[*] --> PendingApproval <<approval>> : Action created,\nautonomy gate requires\nuser approval

PendingApproval --> Approved <<ready>> : User approves\nor autonomy gate\nauto-approves
PendingApproval --> [*] : User rejects\nor action expires

Approved --> Queued <<ready>> : Action enqueued\nfor execution

Queued --> InProgress <<active>> : Worker picks up\njob from queue

InProgress --> NavigatingFlow <<active>> : Browser session\ncreated, executing\nflow steps

NavigatingFlow --> Confirming <<active>> : Final confirmation\nstep reached

Confirming --> Succeeded <<success>> : Cancellation\nconfirmed on\nprovider page
Confirming --> Failed <<failure>> : Confirmation\nstep failed or\ntimed out

NavigatingFlow --> Failed <<failure>> : Flow step failed,\npage state unexpected,\nor CAPTCHA detected

Failed --> RetryScheduled <<retry>> : Retryable failure,\nattempts remaining
Failed --> [*] : Max retries exceeded,\nescalated to manual

RetryScheduled --> Queued <<ready>> : Backoff timer\nexpired, re-queued

Succeeded --> [*] : Savings recorded,\nsubscription updated

note right of PendingApproval
  Created when autonomy
  level is Manual or risk
  score exceeds Supervised
  threshold.
end note

note right of NavigatingFlow
  Steps execute sequentially.
  Screenshots captured at
  each step for audit trail.
end note

note right of RetryScheduled
  Exponential backoff:
  1min, 5min, 30min.
  Max 3 retry attempts.
end note

note right of Succeeded
  Confirmation screenshot
  stored. Subscription status
  updated to Cancelled.
  Savings record created.
end note

@enduml
